info.name: Reddit Blue
info.description:
Reddit Blue is an experimental style intended on adding a bit more color to the site. It's a work in progress and I will be making improvements over time...

IMPORTANT: Similar to a few other Reddit styles, this one will only work if you have disabled custom CSS. To do so, log in, go to preferences and un-tick the checkbox "allow reddits to show me custom styles." You will need to do this or some subreddits will appear broken.
info.additionalInfo:
I've only just started work on this style and will be continuing to refine everything. If you noticed any bugs or have suggestions please let me know and I'll work towards having them included.

New styling coming soon!

Changes:
1.4 (18/04/13)
> Replaced Images with Base 64 code.

1.3 (02/12/12)
> Removed page footer.
> Small colour changes to the Reddit sidebar.

1.2 (16/10/12)
> Moved account links to top of header, away from subreddit content links.
> Adjusted colour and border of post score box and other elements.

1.1 (07/10/12)
>Removed fixed Header.

1.0 (29/09/12)
>Implemented basic styling, including colored header and sidebar. 
>Header is fixed to the top of the page. 
>Compatible with RES. [reddit Enhancement Suite]

If you like what you see, feel free to make a donation through paypal. Will be greatly appreciated!
